**Summary:** This documentation covers the Intercom source integration for Amplitude, which syncs Intercom conversational and user event data to Amplitude using OAuth authentication, with configurable user ID mapping between Intercom User ID or email properties and Amplitude User ID, supporting conversation topics, contact topics, user topics, visitor topics, and event topics with "[Intercom]" event name prefixes.

